explanations.regression: The paper proposes a novel tensor-on-tensor regression model to handle time series of multilayer network data, which involves regression techniques.
explanations.feature representation: The paper uses tensor representation and decomposition of regression coefficients to handle high-dimensionality and heterogeneous impacts, which relates to feature representation.
explanations.representation learning: The tensor representation and decomposition methods used in the paper can be seen as a form of representation learning to capture complex patterns in the data.
